OL,6,FThe man, in his 30s, was taken to
OL,7,Fhospital with a facial injury caused
OL,8,Fby a gunshot to his face. Police say
OL,9,Fhe remains in hospital in a serious
OL,10,Fbut stable condition.JHouse-to-house
OL,11,Finquiries have been carried out and a
OL,12,Fpolice scene is currently in place on
OL,13,FDerbyshire Hill Road while
OL,14,Finvestigations continue.JChief
OL,15,FInspector Tom Welch said: "This is a
OL,16,Fcomplex police investigation, and our
OL,17,Fofficers are still in the very early
OL,18,Fstages of establishing the
OL,19,Fcircumstances of this incident.J"At
OL,20,Fthis stage of our ongoing
OL,21,Finvestigation we can confirm that a
OL,22,Ffirearm was shot in the area causing a
OL,23,Fserious facial injury to a man in his
OL,24,F30s.
