OL,6,F"Therefore, I would appeal to anyone
OL,7,Fwho lives in the area, that has any
OL,8,Finformation or who has doorbell camera
OL,9,Ffootage that may have captured the
OL,10,Fincident to get in touch as soon as
OL,11,Fpossible.J"Information from the public
OL,12,Fis vital if we are to prevent the use
OL,13,Fof firearms which bring misery to our
OL,14,Fstreets and cause such harm in our
OL,15,Fcommunity.J"Our officers remain in the
OL,16,Fsurrounding area of Derbyshire Hill
OL,17,FRoad and are relentless when stopping
OL,18,Fthe use of any firearms or dangerous
OL,19,Fweapons in Merseyside."
